                        <interp inst="t18430703-name-288" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM WINCH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman</hi>). Yesterday morning, at five o'clock, I was in Covent-garden market—I saw the prisoner get into the art, take the coat out, get down, go into Bedford-street, put it on, and then walk up Bedford-street into King-street—I followed him on the opposite side of the way—he saw me looking at him, and turned the other way—I took him to Mr. Bayes, who claimed the coat and comforter.</p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">Property produced and sworn to.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I did not take it out of the cart; I found it in the middle of the road behind the cart.</p>
